#. [message]: speaker=Geobard
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/01_The_Attack_to_Amoran.cfg:288
msgid "Both orcs and bandits have fled! Looks like we won this battle!"
msgstr "オークも山賊も逃げ出したぞ！我々はこの戦いに勝ったようです!"

#. [message]: speaker=Glauco
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/01_The_Attack_to_Amoran.cfg:292
msgid "Not bad, but not enough!"
msgstr "悪くはないが、物足りないな！"

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/01_The_Attack_to_Amoran.cfg:310
msgid "Die, damned orc!"
msgstr "死ね、忌々しいオークめ！"

#. [message]: speaker=Dadoc
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/01_The_Attack_to_Amoran.cfg:314
msgid ""
"That stupid orc got himself killed, I'm not going to come to the same end as "
"him. Let's retire, guys, we'll be back on another occasion, with stronger "
"allies!"
msgstr ""
"あのバカなオークは自分で死んじまった、同じ死に様は晒したくない。おい、引き上"
"げようぜ、またにしよう、もっとツエーのを連れてきてやる！"

#. [message]: speaker=Glauco
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/01_The_Attack_to_Amoran.cfg:332
msgid "The right fate for a wrong man!"
msgstr "悪い奴らの、悪くない結末だな！"

#. [message]: speaker=Grunto
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/01_The_Attack_to_Amoran.cfg:336
msgid ""
"Here's what happens to humans who are too weak! Let's go, guys, we have "
"nothing more to do here, for today at least!"
msgstr ""
"これが、弱すぎる人間がどうなるかの答だよ！さぁ行こうぜ、今日のところは、もう"
"何もすることがないからな！"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/01_The_Attack_to_Amoran.cfg:354
msgid ""
"After many days of battle, the civilians enlisted, not used to fighting, "
"began to desert, frightened and exhausted! The large voids that opened in "
"the lines of the defenders made those who still insisted on fighting even "
"more vulnerable, and soon it was the end!"
msgstr ""
"戦闘が長びいた結果、戦闘に不慣れな市民兵は離脱し始めたり、怯え、疲れ始めたの"
"です！防衛戦線に空いたこの大きな空洞は、戦闘に拘る者たちの戦闘力を更に落ち込"
"ませ、遂には終焉を迎えたのでした！"

#. [message]: speaker=Glauco
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/01_The_Attack_to_Amoran.cfg:360
msgid ""
"I failed my first command! Better to die here than return to Wesnoth like a "
"loser!"
msgstr ""
"人生で初めての指揮だったのに、しくじってしまった！敗者として Wesnoth に戻るよ"
"り、ここで死ぬほうがましだ！"

