#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/02a_Battle_with_the_Bandits.cfg:345
msgid "Kreeee!"
msgstr "キーーッ！"

#. [message]: speaker=Divaid
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/02a_Battle_with_the_Bandits.cfg:349
msgid "Ranfy found somebody!"
msgstr "Ranfy が誰かを見つけた！"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/02a_Battle_with_the_Bandits.cfg:355
msgid "There's someone here!"
msgstr "誰かいる！"

#. [message]: id=Glauco
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/02a_Battle_with_the_Bandits.cfg:403
msgid "There he is! Don't lose sight of it another time!"
msgstr "奴がいるぞ！今度は見失うなよ！"

#. [message]: id=Dadoc
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/02a_Battle_with_the_Bandits.cfg:407
msgid "Find me don't mean catch me!"
msgstr "見つかっても捕まりゃしないぜ！"

#. [message]: speaker=Ranfy
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/02a_Battle_with_the_Bandits.cfg:428
msgid "Kraii?"
msgstr "クラィー？"

#. [message]: speaker=Divaid
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/02a_Battle_with_the_Bandits.cfg:432
msgid ""
"Ranfy found a little bit of gold in that uninhabited house! Probably it was "
"hidden by some bandit."
msgstr "Ranfy があの無人の家で少量の gold を見つけたぞ。"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/02a_Battle_with_the_Bandits.cfg:438
msgid "There's some gold hidden here! Not much, but better than nothing."
msgstr "ここに gold が隠してあるんだ！少量だけど無いよりマシだ。"

#. [message]: speaker=Dadoc
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/02a_Battle_with_the_Bandits.cfg:458
msgid "End of run... for me..."
msgstr "こんな結末なのか、俺様は..."

#. [message]: speaker=Divaid
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/02a_Battle_with_the_Bandits.cfg:468
msgid "Good work, Ranfy!"
msgstr "やるじゃねえか、Ranfy！"

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/02a_Battle_with_the_Bandits.cfg:474
msgid ""
"This is the reward for your crimes, you dirty bandit Dadoc, in the name of "
"all the people of this land!"
msgstr ""
"これは、お前の犯した罪の報いだ、汚い盗っ人 Dadoc め、この土地の全市民の名にお"
"いて！"

#. [message]: speaker=Glauco
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/02a_Battle_with_the_Bandits.cfg:484
msgid ""
"Amoran is more safe, now! This will give us the time to take care of "
"something else!"
msgstr "Amoran はもっと安全だ。さあ、これで他のことに時間が回せるぞ!"

#. [message]: speaker=Dadoc
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/02a_Battle_with_the_Bandits.cfg:506
msgid "Farewell, men of Wesnoth, Dadoc will remain a free man! AH AH AH!"
msgstr "あばよ、 Wesnoth の野郎ども、Dadoc 様は自由に生きてやる！ガッハッハ！"

#. [message]: speaker=Glauco
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/02a_Battle_with_the_Bandits.cfg:510
msgid "Damn, he escaped us. We must return to Amoran as failures!"
msgstr "クッソー、逃げられた。失敗したまま Amoran に戻らねばならんとは！"

