#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/04_The_Bloody_Hills.cfg:318
msgid "Wesnoth Kingdom - Caravan Station n° 1"
msgstr "Wesnoth 王国 キャラバン駅 No.1"

#. [message]: speaker=Mimord
#. I'm assuming the "wrap" referred to here is an article of clothing:
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/04_The_Bloody_Hills.cfg:364
msgid ""
"Damned wolves, I thought I had taught you not to come into my house! Well, "
"I'll make a wrap out of your fur!"
msgstr "くそ狼め、俺の家に入るなと教えたはずだ！お前の毛皮で包んでやる！"

#. [message]: speaker=Croquet
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/04_The_Bloody_Hills.cfg:369
msgid "Hey you! Get your hands off my little Fangy!"
msgstr "おい、お前！俺の Fangy ちゃんに触るな！"

#. [message]: speaker=Mimord
#. a "capon" is a rooster that has been castrated or neutered:
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/04_The_Bloody_Hills.cfg:382
msgid ""
"Ugly bird! Wolves and bats were not enough around here? I'll wring your neck "
"like a capon!"
msgstr ""
"不格好な鳥だな！狼とコウモリだけじゃ飽き足りねえか？ capon（去勢された雄鶏）"
"みたいに首を絞めてやる！"

#. [message]: speaker=Divaid
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/04_The_Bloody_Hills.cfg:387
msgid "Don't you dare to touch my friend Ranfy, tattooed midget!"
msgstr "俺の友達の Ranfy に触るんじゃねえよ、刺青の小人め！"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/04_The_Bloody_Hills.cfg:399
msgid "Urca! House inhabited!"
msgstr "うわっ！　誰か住んでる！"

#. [message]: speaker=Mimord
#. This is about as well as I think I can reword this; I'm not quite sure what he meant by completing his home, but the final sentence is supposed to be a clever way to call the ogre "brainless":
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/04_The_Bloody_Hills.cfg:404
msgid ""
"That's right, stupid ogre! And we were only missing you to complete my home! "
"Well, if I break your head I will not do much damage, as you don't hold "
"anything in there!"
msgstr ""
"その通り、馬鹿なオーガだ！でよ、この家を完成させるにゃ、お前さんが要るんだ"
"よ！ま、お前の頭をカチ割ったところで、ダメージは大して無いだろうさ、中身は"
"空っぽだからな！"

#. [message]: speaker=Geobard
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/04_The_Bloody_Hills.cfg:409
msgid "Wait, that ogre is with us!"
msgstr "待て、仲間の中にはオーガも居るんだぞ！"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/04_The_Bloody_Hills.cfg:415
msgid "Hey! There's somebody here!"
msgstr "おい！誰かここにいるぞ！"

#. [message]: speaker=Glauco
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/04_The_Bloody_Hills.cfg:438
msgid ""
"We passed those hills, finally! We can continue on to reach the nereids now!"
msgstr ""
"やっと丘を越えられた！ これで nereids（ merfolk の一集団）のところへ行けるな!"

#. [message]: speaker=Glauco
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/04_The_Bloody_Hills.cfg:464
msgid ""
"All these attacks are exhausting us; we won't be able to cross the hills! We "
"must retreat; the mission failed!"
msgstr ""
"攻撃を受けたせいで疲弊して、丘を越えられない！撤退しかない、任務失敗だ！"

#. [scenario]: id=05_The_Lizards_Islands
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/05_The_Lizards_Islands.cfg:5
msgid "The Lizard's Islands"
msgstr "トカゲの島"

#. [side]: type=Saurian Flanker, id=Giksy
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/05_The_Lizards_Islands.cfg:60
msgid "Saurian"
msgstr "トカゲ族"

#. [side]: type=Merman Triton, id=Joralda
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/05_The_Lizards_Islands.cfg:80
msgid "Nereids"
msgstr "Nereids（ Merkfolk ）"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#. The inclusion of "Squash" as a synonym for "Defeat" in this objective is for the benefit of Glubtrub:
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/05_The_Lizards_Islands.cfg:102
msgid "Squash... or... Defeat the Saurian Chief"
msgstr "トカゲの首領を倒す"

#. [note]
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/05_The_Lizards_Islands.cfg:119
msgid "The death of $trapper_name will no longer cause defeat."
msgstr "$trapper_name の死は敗北条件ではなくなりました。"

#. [message]: speaker=Giksy
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/05_The_Lizards_Islands.cfg:216
msgid ""
"Let's ssshow them the little sssurprissse that we had prepared for the "
"fisssh if they had decided to recover the issland!"
msgstr ""
"もし、魚たちが、シー島を取り戻すことに決めたら、俺たちが用意シーた小さなサー"
"プライズを見セーてやろうぜ！"

#. [message]: speaker=Giksy
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/05_The_Lizards_Islands.cfg:228
msgid ""
"Thingsss are not going well! Ssshamansss, sssummon other sssnakesss from the "
"sssea!"
msgstr ""
"世の中は、ソそう順調にはいかないぞ！呪術師たちよ、海からもっとヘビを呼び出"
"セー、シャー！"

#. [message]: speaker=Joralda
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/05_The_Lizards_Islands.cfg:235
msgid ""
"More monsters are coming from the north; they're like the ones from before!"
msgstr "北からもっとモンスターがやってきてる、似たような奴らばかりだ！"

#. [message]: speaker=Giksy
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/05_The_Lizards_Islands.cfg:243
msgid "We need of ohtersss sssea companionsss, sssummon all them!"
msgstr "他の海の仲間も必要だ、全員を、ショー喚シーろ、シャー！"

#. [message]: speaker=Geobard
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/05_The_Lizards_Islands.cfg:251
msgid ""
"I hope these are the last ones! They make me feel seasick with all their "
"contortions!"
msgstr ""
"こいつらで最後だといいんだが！クネクネねじ曲がって、船酔いしそうな気分だ！"

#. [message]: speaker=Giksy
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/05_The_Lizards_Islands.cfg:262
msgid "Aaah... I'll... never... sssee... my... treasssure... again..."
msgstr "アァ... もう... 二度とないのか... 俺様の宝物を... 見ることは..."

#. [message]: speaker=Glauco
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/05_The_Lizards_Islands.cfg:295
msgid "Oh no, without the nereids' help, it was all in vain! I failed!"
msgstr "ダ、ダメだ、nereid の助けなしには、すべて水泡に帰してしまう。負けた！"

#. [message]: speaker=Glauco
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/05_The_Lizards_Islands.cfg:306
msgid "It's useless, and we cannot prevail! We failed!"
msgstr "無駄だ、勝てるわけがない！負けた！"

#. [scenario]: id=06_The_Last_Battle
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/06_The_Last_Battle.cfg:5
msgid "The Last Battle"
msgstr "最後の戦い"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/06_The_Last_Battle.cfg:38
msgid "Defeat Gan-Tarkas"
msgstr "Gan-Tarkas を倒す"

#. [message]: speaker=Gan-Tarkas
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/06_The_Last_Battle.cfg:311
msgid "Widen the path across the river again, and then everyone attack!"
msgstr "川を渡る道をもう一度広げるんだ、そうして全員攻撃だ！"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/06_The_Last_Battle.cfg:451
msgid "Defeat all enemy leaders"
msgstr "敵のリーダーをすべて倒す"

#. [message]: speaker=Geobard
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/06_The_Last_Battle.cfg:483
msgid "Those damned are all dead or escaped! Finally we finished!"
msgstr "あの忌々しい奴らは、全滅したか逃げ出したかだ！　遂に終わった！"

#. [message]: speaker=Gan-Tarkas
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/06_The_Last_Battle.cfg:499
msgid "Impossible!"
msgstr "あり得ん！"

#. [message]: speaker=Glauco
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/06_The_Last_Battle.cfg:503
msgid "With your end, orc, Amoran can and will have a new start!"
msgstr "オークさんよ、お前らが消えて、Amoran は新しいスタートを切れるんだよ！"

#. [message]: speaker=Glubtrub
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/06_The_Last_Battle.cfg:518
msgid "To remain only to squash big snake!"
msgstr "大きなヘビ潰すためだけに、オレ、残る！"

#. [message]: speaker=Hisskss
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/06_The_Last_Battle.cfg:534
msgid "Hissss!"
msgstr "シャーーーッ！"

#. [message]: speaker=Glubtrub
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/06_The_Last_Battle.cfg:542
msgid "Other snake make flat-flat! Oh! Oh! Oh!"
msgstr "他のヘビ、みんな静かにしてるでしょ、こら！オゥオゥオゥ！"

#. [message]: speaker=Geobard
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/06_The_Last_Battle.cfg:551
msgid "And now let's finish taking care of his friend, Gan-Tarkas!"
msgstr "さて、それじゃ、彼のご友人、 Gan-Tarkas を始末する番だ！"

#. [scenario]: id=07_Epilogue
#: A_Little_Adventure/scenarios/07_Epilogue.cfg:5
msgid "Epilogue"
msgstr "エピローグ"

#. [unit_type]: id=Merman Brawler, race=merman
#: A_Little_Adventure/units/Brawler.cfg:5
msgid "Merman Brawler"
msgstr "Merman Brawler"

#. [unit_type]: id=Merman Brawler, race=merman
#. Brawlers are also in Dead Water; try to keep the description similar:
#: A_Little_Adventure/units/Brawler.cfg:19
msgid ""
"Exceptionally large and strong mermen are sometimes more comfortable with "
"their own fists and tails than with other weapons."
msgstr ""
"並外れた大きさと強さを持つマーマンは、時に他の武器よりも、自分の拳や尻尾を気"
"持ちよく使いこなします。"

#. [attack]: type=impact
#: A_Little_Adventure/units/Brawler.cfg:36
#: A_Little_Adventure/units/Citizen.cfg:36
msgid "fist"
msgstr "拳"

#. [attack]: type=impact
#: A_Little_Adventure/units/Brawler.cfg:44
msgid "tail"
msgstr "尾びれ"

#. [set_variable]
#: A_Little_Adventure/units/Brawler.cfg:112
#: A_Little_Adventure/units/Brawler.cfg:174
